parameters:
Prison Guard: What the hell... Scaring me like that, you've
got some nerve! At this hour, all the rats should be in
their cells, right?

(This is bad... I need to do something, at least until my
companions have time to hide...!)

Actually, I've been given a job by the boss you know so well
here.

I was sent to show my appreciation for your hard work, but
that alone wouldn't be fun, right? So I prepared others to
give you a little surprise as an extra treat.

It was supposed to be just a light jab, but it seems they
couldn't hold back. But with your sturdy body, you should be
fine, right?

No need to worry about them. Once they're done, they'll just
go back to their cells.

So how about it? Are you pissed off? I want you to release
that irritation, that overflowing desire, unleash it all on
my body.
I prefer it rough too. So, come on... Please...

Prison Guard: Hehehe, is that so. If it's a gift from the
boss, I can't refuse. It's rare for that bastard to send
over something he's claimed as his own, but it seems you've
done quite well.

Prison Guard: You've got some peculiar tastes. Well then, as
you wish, I'll make it rough. Make sure the others get a
good view... Here I come!!

That's good... I'm begging you... Ah... Aguh... Inside me...
Nngh...! Release your seed... Oh... with all your might...
pour it out...!
Ugh! Uguh...! Hah! Hah! Ah... Aaahhhhh...!!!
